---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | coolLabs">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg">
            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    <strong>Last Updated</strong>: March 23, 2025
                </p>
                <p>
                    At coolLabs Technologies Bt. ("we", "us", or "our"), we
                    create services and applications ("products") under the
                    domains coollabs.io, coolify.io, and all subdomains,
                    designed to keep your online information secure and private.
                    We operate these platforms and are committed to not
                    transferring your data to any external company unless
                    required by law.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    Our products may include links to external sites not
                    operated by us. Please be aware that we have no control over
                    their content or privacy practices, and this policy does not
                    apply to them.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    What Information We Collect
                </h2>
                <p>
                    To make our products functional, we collect only the
                    following basic information during registration:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
                    <li>Your email address</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-2">
                    We don't collect anything beyond what's necessary for our
                    services, and we anonymize data whenever technically
                    possible.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    How We Use Your Information
                </h2>
                <p>We use your email address to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
                    <li>Create and manage your account</li>
                    <li>
                        Communicate with you about your account or our services
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Send optional updates or promotions (only with your
                        consent)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    Legal Basis for Processing
                </h2>
                <p>We process your email address based on:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Consent</strong>: You agree to this when you
                        register, and you can withdraw consent anytime
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Contract</strong>: It's necessary to provide the
                        services you've requested
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    How We Protect Your Information
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We store your email address securely using encryption and
                    access controls to prevent unauthorized access. We keep it
                    only as long as needed to provide your requested service, or
                    as required by law. Once no longer needed, we delete it
                    securely.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    Sharing Your Information
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We do not share your information with third parties, except
                    when legally required (e.g., by a court order).
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have control over your data. Under GDPR, you can:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Access</strong>: Request a copy of your data
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Correct</strong>: Update inaccurate information
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Delete</strong>: Remove your data from our
                        servers
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Restrict</strong>: Limit how we use your data
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Portability</strong>: Get your data in a usable
                        format
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Object</strong>: Stop processing (e.g., for
                        marketing)
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    To exercise these rights or withdraw consent, use the
                    deletion option in our products or contact us.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
                <p>Questions about data handling? Reach out to us:</p>
                <ul class="list-none mt-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Email</strong>: <a
                            href="mailto:privacy@coollabs.io"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
                            >privacy@coollabs.io</a
                        >
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>More Info</strong>: <a
                            href="https://coolify.io/docs/contact"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"
                            >https://coolify.io/docs/contact</a
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    Changes to This Policy
                </h2>
                <p>
                    If we update this policy, we'll post the new version on our
                    websites and notify you via email or within our products.
                    Continued use of our services means you accept the updated
                    policy.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
